title_full:
Rat Section

              —
              What Stays In Vegas
            
              (Halcyon Veil)
label: Halcyon Veil
description:
Billed as a long-in-hiatus industrial art act whose catalog is now lost and/or inaccessible, Rat Section is a London duo whose Halcyon Veil debut is a sardonic sprawl of blistered warehouse thuds, tweezed vocals and punky, electroid noise.

Rat Section's mythical backstory is immediately unravelled by their press pics - if you're gonna tell us you've been releasing records since the '80s, then please reveal yer skincare routine cuz we ain't buying it. But despite the subterfuge, 'What Stays in Vegas' is... more
